hat what was given in someone’s charge is doomed to perish</biblScope></bibl></cit></cit></re><cit type="exampleGroup" corresp="#sense_." n=""><cit type="example"><quote>ūj bærny næ bacæwʒynæn</quote><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>я не возьму этого на свою ответственность</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>I will not take this under my responsibility</q></cit></cit><cit type="example"><quote>wacajrægtæ rakænyn ta — mæ bærn</quote><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>забрать пленных — на моей ответственности</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>take prisoners is my responsibility</q></cit><bibl><ref target="#src_Хар._Кадӕг"/><biblScope>56</biblScope></bibl></cit></cit><etym xml:lang="ru">Производное от <xr><ref target="#entry_bar"/></xr> ‘право’, ‘власть’, ‘воля’; суффикс -%in%i = <mentioned xml:lang="x-oldirn"><lang/><w>-na-</w></mentioned>, ср. %ibæzn%i [см. <xr><ref target="#entry_bæz-"/></xr>, д. %b%ixeznæ%i%b [см. <xr/>], д. <xr><ref target="#entry_arǧævnæ"/></xr>, д. færæznæ [см. <xr><ref target="#entry_færæz"/></xr>]. Ослабление гласного основы обычно (%iа%i →%iæ%i). См. <xr><ref target="#entry_bar"/></xr>. Ср. д. <xr><ref target="#entry_bæragæ"/></xr>.%n<bibl corresp="#ref_ОЯФ_I"><biblScope>574</biblScope></bibl>.</etym><etym xml:lang="en">The word is derived from <xr><ref target="#entry_bar"/></xr> ‘right’, ‘power’, ‘will’; the suffix -%in%i = <mentioned xml:lang="x-oldirn"><lang/><w>-na-</w></mentioned>, cf. %ibæzn%i [see <xr><ref target="#entry_bæz-"/></xr>], Digor %b%ixeznæ%i%b [see <xr><ref target="#entry_xeznæ"/></xr>], Digor <xr><ref target="#entry_arǧævnæ"/></xr>, Digor %ifæræznæ%i [see <xr><ref target="#entry_færæz"/></xr>]. The weakening of the vowel is regular (%iа%i →%iæ%i). See <xr><ref target="#entry_bar"/></xr>. Cf. Digor <xr><ref target="#entry_bæragæ"/></xr>.%n<bibl corresp="#ref_ОЯФ_I"><biblScope>574</biblScope></bibl>.</etym></entry>